  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Toast the bread slices until lightly browned.",
    "Spread a layer of Dijon mustard on each toasted bread slice.",
    "Top each bread slice with a halved vine tomato.",
    "Sprinkle shredded low-fat mozzarella cheese over the tomatoes.",
    "Drizzle low-sodium butter over the cheese.",
    "Season with salt-free seasoning blend and black pepper.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
